@startuml Sequence_Admin_CompanyVerification
title Quản Trị - Xác Thực Công Ty

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant CompanyService as "Company\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Danh Sách Công Ty Chờ Xác Thực ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Xác thực công ty"
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: GET /api/admin/companies/pending?page=0&size=20
CompanyService -> Database: Query cong_ty (status=PENDING)
Database --> CompanyService: Return list
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Companies list
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị danh sách

== Xem Chi Tiết Công Ty ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click vào công ty
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: GET /api/admin/companies/{companyId}
CompanyService -> Database: Get company details
Database --> CompanyService: Company info
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Full details
FrontEnd --> Admin: Xem chi tiết\n(tên, tax ID, địa chỉ)

== Kiểm Tra Mã Số Thuế ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Kiểm tra MST"
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: POST /api/admin/companies/{companyId}/verify-tax-id
CompanyService -> CompanyService: Validate tax ID format
CompanyService -> Database: Check tax ID unique
Database --> CompanyService: OK
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Tax ID valid
FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ MST hợp lệ

== Phê Duyệt Công Ty ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Phê duyệt"
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: POST /api/admin/companies/{companyId}/approve
CompanyService -> Database: Update status = VERIFIED
Database --> CompanyService: OK
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Approved
FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Phê duyệt thành công

== Từ Chối Công Ty ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Từ chối"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show reason form
Admin -> FrontEnd: Nhập lý do từ chối
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: POST /api/admin/companies/{companyId}/reject\n(reason)
CompanyService -> Database: Update status = REJECTED
Database --> CompanyService: OK
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Rejected
FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Từ chối thành công

== Cấm Công Ty ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Cấm công ty"
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: POST /api/admin/companies/{companyId}/ban
CompanyService -> Database: Update status = BANNED
Database --> CompanyService: OK
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Banned
FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Cấm công ty thành công

@enduml
